To set up my working environment in Scheme, I used:
-   Petite Chez Scheme, version 8.4
-   "mk.scm" from http://kanren.cvs.sourceforge.net/kanren/kanren/mini/mk.scm
-   "mkextraforms.scm" from
    http://kanren.cvs.sourceforge.net/kanren/kanren/mini/mkextraforms.scm

The last two files are loaded at the top of my code-along record, "mini.scm".

See also
-   http://minikanren.org/
-   http://kanren.sourceforge.net/
-   https://github.com/miniKanren/miniKanren
